  "2026-04-03T18:07:42.651Z",codex-agent,Task created for implementation of validate command and close validation modes.
  "2026-04-03T18:55:47.266Z",codex-agent,"Implemented standalone pm validate plus pm close --validate-close (warn/strict), wired completion/help/contracts/Pi parity, and added integration/unit coverage including full validate branch-gate tests."
  "2026-04-03T18:55:47.832Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/validate-command.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed (31/31)."
  "2026-04-05T01:12:16.602Z",codex-agent,"Reopened for Issue 6 follow-up: add validate fail mode flags so automation can opt into non-zero exit when validate result ok=false while preserving default compatibility."
  "2026-04-05T02:18:54.642Z",codex-agent,"Issue 6 follow-up completed: pm validate now supports non-default warning-fail exits via --strict-exit and --fail-on-warn while keeping default behavior compatible. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/validate-command.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts passed; repro probes show status=1 for both strict-exit and fail-on-warn in tracked-all-strict mode; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed (branch 91.01%); pnpm build passed."
